overview:
Venture Fund is a global online Mentoring & Funding platform for great ideas and start up communities.

Venture Fund’s primary objective is to mentor and fund quality ideas and start ups by introducing them to qualified investors from around the world.

Venture Fund has been set up by global entrepreneurs who have built successful and scalable businesses ranging from entertainment and film, mobile applications and VAS services, e-commerce’s and social networking. Their 100+ year combined vast wealth of experience is something they wish to pass back and bring to market an on-line organized and simple way of connecting entrepreneurs to investors by creating the world’s largest start up funding community.
